import React from 'react'

import { AppSvgContainer } from './AppSvgContainer'
import { THEME } from '../../../theme'


export const AppChevronIcon = ({ color = THEME.FONT_COLOR }) => (
  <AppSvgContainer
    width="8"
    height="5"
    viewBoxWidth="8"
    viewBoxHeight="6"
  >
    <path
      d="M0.5 0.5L4.5 5.5L8.5 0.5"
      stroke={ color }
      strokeLinecap="round"
    />
  </AppSvgContainer>
)
